org.jboss.aerogear.sync

Interface DataStore<T,S extends Edit<? extends Diff>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the Document that this data store can store.
    S - The type of Edits that this data store can store
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClientDataStore<T,S>, ServerDataStore<T,S>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientInMemoryDataStore, ServerInMemoryDataStore

    public interface DataStore<T,S extends Edit<? extends Diff>>
    A DataStore implementation is responible for storing and serving data for a Differential Synchronization implementation.
